JavaScript Method for Refreshing Relationship Graphs:
If you embed a Relationship Graph in another Lightning Web Component, you can use the JavaScript refreshGraph method to refresh the Relationship Graph.
Relationship Graph Node Filter Operators:
Supported operators are equals, not equals, like, greater than, greater than or equal, less than, and less than or equal.
Timeline Graphs Support One-to-Many Relationships:
In this release, Timeline graphs also support one-to-many relationships.
